<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>29</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>shéi shì mù yáng rén 迦南29</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 fēng yǔ zhōng yǒu nǐ de shēn yǐng, měi tiáo lù shàng liú xià nǐ de jiǎo bù shēng;
 pī xīng dài jiǎo bù cōng cōng, jīn tiān běi shān gǔ míng tiān yòu shàng nán shān lǐng.
 rì rì yuè yuè chūn xià qiū dōng, yáng de hǎo mù rén bù shì gù gōng.
 yī kē xīn wèi zhǔ jiā jǐn zhōng, yī kē gǔn tàng de xīn zhì sǐ zhōng chéng;
 mí yáng liú lí xiǎo yáng āi míng, mù yáng rén de xīn zhōng zěn néng ān dìng?
 shéi shì mù yáng rén, shéi shì mù yáng rén, zhǔ kàn dé qīng.</lyrics>
</song>